{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"Many of you could ask the question, you know,"},{"time":3000,"text":"why is a flying car, or maybe more accurately,"},{"time":6000,"text":"a roadable aircraft, possible at this time?"},{"time":10000,"text":"A number of years ago,"},{"time":12000,"text":"Mr. Ford predicted that flying cars"},{"time":14000,"text":"of some form would be available."},{"time":16000,"text":"Now, 60 years later,"},{"time":18000,"text":"I'm here to tell you why it's possible."},{"time":20000,"text":"When I was about five years old,"},{"time":22000,"text":"not very much -- about a year after"},{"time":24000,"text":"Mr. Ford made his predictions,"},{"time":26000,"text":"I was living in a rural part of Canada,"},{"time":29000,"text":"on the side of a mountain in a very isolated area."},{"time":34000,"text":"Getting to school, for a kid that was actually pretty short for his age,"},{"time":38000,"text":"through the Canadian winter, was not a pleasant experience."},{"time":41000,"text":"It was a trying and scary thing"},{"time":45000,"text":"for a young kid to be going through."}]},{"cues":[{"time":48000,"text":"At the end of my first year in school, in the summer of that year,"},{"time":53000,"text":"I discovered a couple hummingbirds"},{"time":56000,"text":"that were caught in a shed near my home."},{"time":58000,"text":"They'd worn themselves out,"},{"time":60000,"text":"beating themselves against the window,"},{"time":62000,"text":"and, well, they were easy to capture."},{"time":64000,"text":"I took them outside and as I let them go, that split second, even though they were very tired,"},{"time":68000,"text":"that second I let them go they hovered for a second,"},{"time":70000,"text":"then zipped off into the distance."},{"time":72000,"text":"I thought, what a great way to get to school."}]},{"cues":[{"time":74000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":77000,"text":"For a kid at that age, this was like infinite speed, disappearing,"},{"time":81000,"text":"and I was very inspired by that."},{"time":83000,"text":"And so the next -- over the next"},{"time":85000,"text":"six decades, believe it or not,"},{"time":87000,"text":"I've built a number of aircraft,"},{"time":90000,"text":"with the goal of creating something that could do for you, or me,"},{"time":94000,"text":"what the hummingbird does,"},{"time":96000,"text":"and give you that flexibility."},{"time":99000,"text":"I've called this vehicle, generically, a volantor,"},{"time":103000,"text":"after the Latin word \"volant,\" meaning,"},{"time":105000,"text":"to fly in a light, nimble manner."},{"time":108000,"text":"Volantor-like helicopter, perhaps."},{"time":110000,"text":"The FAA, the controlling body above all,"},{"time":113000,"text":"calls it a \"powered lift aircraft.\""},{"time":116000,"text":"And they've actually issued a pilot's license --"},{"time":119000,"text":"a powerlift pilot's license -- for this type of aircraft."},{"time":123000,"text":"It's closer than you think. It's kind of remarkable when you consider that"},{"time":126000,"text":"there are no operational powered lift aircraft."},{"time":129000,"text":"So for once, perhaps, the government is ahead of itself."}]},{"cues":[{"time":133000,"text":"The press calls my particular volantor a \"Skycar.\""},{"time":138000,"text":"This is a little bit earlier version of it,"},{"time":141000,"text":"that's why it's given the X designation,"},{"time":143000,"text":"but it's a four-passenger aircraft"},{"time":145000,"text":"that could take off vertically, like a helicopter --"},{"time":147000,"text":"therefore it doesn't need an airfield."},{"time":149000,"text":"On the ground, it's powered electrically."},{"time":153000,"text":"It's actually classified as a motorcycle"},{"time":156000,"text":"because of the three wheels, which is a great asset"},{"time":158000,"text":"because it allows you, theoretically, to use this on the highways"},{"time":160000,"text":"in most states, and actually in all cities."},{"time":163000,"text":"So that's an asset because if you've got to deal with the crash protection issues"},{"time":166000,"text":"of the automobile, forget it -- you're never going to fly it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":170000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":175000,"text":"One could say that a helicopter"},{"time":177000,"text":"does pretty much what the hummingbird does,"},{"time":180000,"text":"and gets around in much the same way, and it's true,"},{"time":182000,"text":"but a helicopter is a very complex device."},{"time":186000,"text":"It's expensive --"},{"time":188000,"text":"so expensive that very few people could own or use it."},{"time":192000,"text":"It's often been described because of its fragile nature and its complexity,"},{"time":196000,"text":"as a series of parts -- a large number of parts --"},{"time":198000,"text":"flying in formation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":200000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":205000,"text":"Another difference, and I have to describe this,"},{"time":207000,"text":"because it's very personal,"},{"time":209000,"text":"another great difference between the helicopter"},{"time":211000,"text":"and the volantor --"},{"time":213000,"text":"in my case the Skycar volantor --"},{"time":215000,"text":"is the experience that I've had"},{"time":217000,"text":"in flying both of those."},{"time":219000,"text":"In a helicopter you feel -- and it's still a remarkable sensation --"},{"time":222000,"text":"you feel like you're being hauled up from above"},{"time":225000,"text":"by a vibrating crane."},{"time":227000,"text":"When you get in the Skycar -- and I can tell you,"},{"time":229000,"text":"there's only one other person that's flown it, but he had the same sensation --"},{"time":232000,"text":"you really feel like you're being lifted up"},{"time":234000,"text":"by a magic carpet,"},{"time":237000,"text":"without any vibration whatsoever. The sensation is unbelievable."},{"time":240000,"text":"And it's been a great motivator."},{"time":242000,"text":"I only get to fly this vehicle occasionally,"},{"time":245000,"text":"and only when I can persuade my stockholders"},{"time":247000,"text":"to let me do so,"},{"time":249000,"text":"but it's still one of those wonderful experiences"},{"time":252000,"text":"that reward you for all that time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":258000,"text":"What we really need is something to replace the automobile"},{"time":261000,"text":"for those 50-plus mile trips."},{"time":264000,"text":"Very few people realize that 50 mile-plus trips"},{"time":266000,"text":"make up 85 percent of the miles traveled in America."},{"time":269000,"text":"If we can get rid of that,"},{"time":271000,"text":"then the highways will now be useful to you,"},{"time":274000,"text":"as contrasted by what's happening"},{"time":276000,"text":"in many parts of the world today."},{"time":280000,"text":"On this next slide, is an interesting history"},{"time":284000,"text":"of what we really have seen in infrastructure,"},{"time":288000,"text":"because whether I give you a perfect Skycar,"},{"time":291000,"text":"the perfect vehicle for use, it's going to have very little value to you"},{"time":294000,"text":"unless you've got a system to use it in."},{"time":296000,"text":"I'm sure any of you have asked the question,"},{"time":298000,"text":"yeah, are there great things up there -- what am I going to do, get up there?"},{"time":300000,"text":"It's bad enough on a highway, what's it going to be like to be in the air?"},{"time":303000,"text":"This world that you're going to be talking about tomorrow"},{"time":306000,"text":"is going to be completely integrated. You're not going to be a pilot,"},{"time":308000,"text":"you're going to be a passenger."},{"time":310000,"text":"And it's the infrastructure that really determines whether this process goes forward."}]},{"cues":[{"time":313000,"text":"I can tell you, technically we can build Skycars --"},{"time":315000,"text":"my God, we went to the moon!"},{"time":317000,"text":"The technology there was much more difficult than what I'm dealing with here."},{"time":320000,"text":"But we have to have these priority changes,"},{"time":322000,"text":"we have to have infrastructure to go with this."},{"time":324000,"text":"Historically you see that we got around"},{"time":326000,"text":"200 years ago by canals,"},{"time":328000,"text":"and as that system disappeared, were replaced by railroads."},{"time":331000,"text":"As that disappeared we came in with highways."},{"time":333000,"text":"But if you look at that top corner -- the highway system --"},{"time":336000,"text":"you see where we are today. Highways are no longer being built,"},{"time":340000,"text":"and that's a fact. You won't see any additional highways"},{"time":343000,"text":"in the next 10 years."},{"time":345000,"text":"However, the next 10 years, if like the last 10 years,"},{"time":347000,"text":"we're going to see 30 percent more traffic."},{"time":350000,"text":"And where is that going to lead you to?"},{"time":352000,"text":"So the issue then, I've often asked, is"},{"time":354000,"text":"when is it going to happen?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":357000,"text":"When are we going to be able to have these vehicles?"},{"time":360000,"text":"And of course, if you ask me, I'm going to give you a really optimistic view."},{"time":363000,"text":"After all, I've been spending 60 years here believing it's going to happen tomorrow."},{"time":366000,"text":"So, I'm not going to quote myself on this."},{"time":369000,"text":"I'd prefer to quote someone else,"},{"time":371000,"text":"who testified with me before Congress,"},{"time":373000,"text":"and in his position as head of NASA"},{"time":377000,"text":"put forward this particular vision"},{"time":379000,"text":"of the future of this type of aircraft."},{"time":383000,"text":"Now I would argue, actually, if you look at the fact that on the highways today,"},{"time":386000,"text":"you're only averaging about 30 miles per hour --"},{"time":389000,"text":"on average, according to the DOT --"},{"time":392000,"text":"the Skycar travels at over 300 miles an hour,"},{"time":394000,"text":"up to 25,000 feet."},{"time":397000,"text":"And so, in effect, you could see perhaps a tenfold increase"},{"time":399000,"text":"in the ability to get around"},{"time":402000,"text":"as far as speed is concerned."}]},{"cues":[{"time":409000,"text":"Unbeknownst to many of you,"},{"time":412000,"text":"the highway in the sky that I'm talking about here"},{"time":414000,"text":"has been under construction for 10 years."},{"time":417000,"text":"It makes use of the GPS -- you're familiar with GPS in your automobile,"},{"time":420000,"text":"but you may not be familiar with the fact that there's a GPS U.S.,"},{"time":423000,"text":"there's a Russian GPS,"},{"time":425000,"text":"and there's a new GPS system"},{"time":427000,"text":"going to Europe, called Galileo."},{"time":429000,"text":"With those three systems,"},{"time":431000,"text":"you have what is always necessary --"},{"time":433000,"text":"a level of redundancy that says,"},{"time":435000,"text":"if one system fails, you'll still have a way"},{"time":437000,"text":"to make sure that you're being controlled."},{"time":439000,"text":"Because if you're in this world, where computers are controlling what you're doing,"},{"time":442000,"text":"it's going to be very critical that something can't fail on you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":447000,"text":"How would a trip in a Skycar work?"},{"time":449000,"text":"Well, you can't right now"},{"time":451000,"text":"take off from your home because it's too noisy."},{"time":454000,"text":"I mean to be able to take off from your home, you'd have to be extremely quiet."},{"time":457000,"text":"But it's still fairly quiet."},{"time":459000,"text":"You'd motor, electrically, to a vertiport,"},{"time":463000,"text":"which may be a few blocks, maybe even a few miles away."},{"time":465000,"text":"This is clearly, as I said earlier, a roadable aircraft,"},{"time":468000,"text":"and you're not going to spend that much time on the road."},{"time":470000,"text":"After all, if you can fly like that,"},{"time":472000,"text":"why are you going to drive around on a highway?"},{"time":474000,"text":"Go to a local vertiport,"},{"time":476000,"text":"plug in your destination,"},{"time":479000,"text":"delivered almost like a passenger."},{"time":483000,"text":"You can play computer games, you can sleep, you can read on the way."},{"time":487000,"text":"This is the world -- there won't be you as a pilot. And I know the pilots in the audience aren't going to like that --\n"},{"time":490000,"text":"and I've had a lot of bad feedback"},{"time":492000,"text":"from people who want to be up there, flying around"},{"time":494000,"text":"and experiencing that."},{"time":497000,"text":"And of course, I suppose like recreational parks you can still do that."},{"time":500000,"text":"But the vehicle itself is going to be a very, very controlled environment."},{"time":504000,"text":"Or it's going to have no use to you as a person who might use such a system."}]},{"cues":[{"time":508000,"text":"We flew the first vehicle for the international press \n"},{"time":511000,"text":"in 1965, when I really got it started."},{"time":513000,"text":"I was a professor at the U.C. Davis System,"},{"time":515000,"text":"and I got a lot of excitement around this,"},{"time":517000,"text":"and I was able to fund the initiation of the program back in that time."},{"time":521000,"text":"And then through the various years"},{"time":523000,"text":"we invented various vehicles."},{"time":525000,"text":"Actually the critical point was in 1989,"},{"time":528000,"text":"when we demonstrated the stability of this vehicle --"},{"time":530000,"text":"how completely stable it was in all circumstances,"},{"time":533000,"text":"which is of course very critical."},{"time":535000,"text":"Still not a practical vehicle during all of this,"},{"time":538000,"text":"but moving in the right direction, we believe."},{"time":542000,"text":"Finally, in the early part of --"},{"time":545000,"text":"or actually the middle of 2002,"},{"time":549000,"text":"we flew the 400 -- M400, which was the four-passenger vehicle."},{"time":553000,"text":"In this case here, we're flying it remotely, as we always did at the beginning."},{"time":557000,"text":"And we had very small power plants in it at this time."},{"time":560000,"text":"We are now installing larger powerplants,"},{"time":562000,"text":"which will make it possible for me to get back on board."}]},{"cues":[{"time":564000,"text":"A vertical-takeoff aircraft"},{"time":566000,"text":"is not the safest vehicle during the test flight program."},{"time":570000,"text":"There's an old adage that applied for the years"},{"time":573000,"text":"between 1950s and 1970s,"},{"time":576000,"text":"when every aeronautical company"},{"time":578000,"text":"was working on vertical-takeoff aircraft."},{"time":582000,"text":"A vertical-takeoff aircraft"},{"time":584000,"text":"needs an artificial stabilization system --"},{"time":586000,"text":"that's essential."},{"time":588000,"text":"At least for the hover,"},{"time":590000,"text":"and the low-speed flight."},{"time":594000,"text":"If that single-stability system,"},{"time":596000,"text":"that brain that flies that aircraft, fails, or if the engine fails,"},{"time":600000,"text":"that vehicle crashes. There is no option to that."},{"time":603000,"text":"And the adage that I'm referring to,"},{"time":605000,"text":"that applied at that time,"},{"time":607000,"text":"was that nothing comes down faster"},{"time":609000,"text":"than a VTOL aircraft upside down."}]},{"cues":[{"time":611000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":613000,"text":"That's a macabre comment because we lost a lot of pilots."},{"time":616000,"text":"In fact, the aircraft companies gave up on"},{"time":618000,"text":"vertical-takeoff aircraft"},{"time":620000,"text":"more or less for a number of years."},{"time":622000,"text":"And there's really only one operational aircraft in the world today"},{"time":625000,"text":"that's a vertical-takeoff aircraft -- as distinct from a helicopter --"},{"time":627000,"text":"and that's the Hawker Harrier jump jet."},{"time":635000,"text":"A vertical-takeoff aircraft,"},{"time":637000,"text":"like the hummingbird,"},{"time":639000,"text":"has a very high metabolism,"},{"time":641000,"text":"which means it requires a lot of energy."},{"time":644000,"text":"Getting that energy is very, very difficult. It all comes down"},{"time":647000,"text":"to that power plant -- how to get a large amount of power in a small package."}]},{"cues":[{"time":653000,"text":"Fortunately, Dr. Felix Wankel"},{"time":655000,"text":"invented the rotary engine."},{"time":658000,"text":"A very unique engine -- it's round,"},{"time":660000,"text":"it's small, it's vibration-free."},{"time":663000,"text":"It fits exactly where we need to fit it,"},{"time":665000,"text":"right in the center of the hubs of the ducts in the system --"},{"time":668000,"text":"very critical. In fact that engine --"},{"time":670000,"text":"for those who are into the automobile --"},{"time":672000,"text":"know that it recently is applied to the RX8 --"},{"time":674000,"text":"the Mazda."},{"time":676000,"text":"And that sportscar won Sports Car of the Year."},{"time":680000,"text":"Wonderful engine."},{"time":682000,"text":"In that application, it generates one horsepower per pound,"},{"time":684000,"text":"which is twice as good as your car engine today,"},{"time":687000,"text":"but only half of what we need."},{"time":689000,"text":"My company has spent 35 years"},{"time":692000,"text":"and many millions of dollars taking that rotary engine,"},{"time":695000,"text":"which was invented in the late '50s, and getting it to the point that we get"},{"time":698000,"text":"over two horsepower per pound, reliably, and critical."},{"time":701000,"text":"We actually get 175 horsepower"},{"time":704000,"text":"into one cubic foot."},{"time":707000,"text":"We have eight engines in this vehicle."},{"time":709000,"text":"We have four computers. We have two parachutes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":713000,"text":"Redundancy is the critical issue here."},{"time":715000,"text":"If you want to stay alive you've got to have backups."},{"time":717000,"text":"And we have actually flown this vehicle and lost an engine,"},{"time":719000,"text":"and continued to hover."},{"time":721000,"text":"The computers back up each other. There's a voting system --"},{"time":724000,"text":"if one computer is not agreeing with the other three,"},{"time":728000,"text":"it's kicked out of the system."},{"time":729000,"text":"And then you have three -- you still have the triple redundancy."},{"time":732000,"text":"If one of those fails, you still have a second chance."},{"time":735000,"text":"If you stick around, then good luck."},{"time":737000,"text":"There won't be a third chance."},{"time":741000,"text":"The parachutes are there -- hopefully,"},{"time":743000,"text":"more for psychological than real reasons, but"},{"time":746000,"text":"they will be an ultimate backup if it comes to that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":749000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":752000,"text":"I'd like to show you an animation in this next one,"},{"time":754000,"text":"which is one element"},{"time":756000,"text":"of the Skycar's use,"},{"time":758000,"text":"but it's one that demonstrates how it could be used."},{"time":760000,"text":"You could think of it personally in your own terms,"},{"time":762000,"text":"of how you might use it."},{"time":764000,"text":"Video: Skycar dispatched, launch rescue vehicle for San Francisco."},{"time":796000,"text":"Paul Moller: I believe that personal transportation"},{"time":798000,"text":"in something like the Skycar,"},{"time":800000,"text":"probably in another volantor form as well,"},{"time":803000,"text":"will be a significant part of our lives,"},{"time":806000,"text":"as Dr. Goldin says, within the next 10 years."},{"time":809000,"text":"And it's going to change the demographics in a very significant way."},{"time":813000,"text":"If you can live 75 miles from San Francisco and get there in 15 minutes,"},{"time":817000,"text":"you're going to sell your 700,000-dollar apartment,"},{"time":821000,"text":"buy an upscale home on the side of a mountain,"},{"time":823000,"text":"buy a Skycar,"},{"time":825000,"text":"which I think would be priced at that time perhaps"},{"time":827000,"text":"in the area of 100,000 dollars, put money in the bank ..."},{"time":830000,"text":"that's a very significant incentive for getting out of San Francisco."},{"time":834000,"text":"But you better be the first one out of town as the real estate values go to hell."}]},{"cues":[{"time":837000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":842000,"text":"Developing the Skycar has been a real challenge."},{"time":845000,"text":"Obviously I'm dependent on a lot of other people"},{"time":847000,"text":"believing in what I'm doing -- both financially and in technical help."},{"time":851000,"text":"And that has --"},{"time":853000,"text":"you run into situations where you have this great acceptance of what you're doing,"},{"time":857000,"text":"and a lot of rejection of the same kind of thing."},{"time":860000,"text":"I characterized this emerging technology"},{"time":864000,"text":"in an aphorism,"},{"time":866000,"text":"as it's described,"},{"time":869000,"text":"which really talks about what I've experienced,"},{"time":871000,"text":"and I'm sure what other people may have experienced"},{"time":873000,"text":"in emerging technologies."}]},{"cues":[{"time":881000,"text":"There's an interesting poll that came out recently"},{"time":883000,"text":"under NAS --"},{"time":885000,"text":"I think it's MSNBC --"},{"time":887000,"text":"in which they asked the question,"},{"time":889000,"text":"\"Are you in the market for a volantor?\""},{"time":892000,"text":"Twenty-three percent said, \"Yes, as soon as possible.\""},{"time":895000,"text":"Forty-seven percent -- yes, as soon as they could -- price could come down."},{"time":898000,"text":"Twenty-three percent said, \"As soon as it's proven safe.\""},{"time":901000,"text":"Only seven percent said"},{"time":903000,"text":"that they wouldn't consider buying a Skycar."},{"time":906000,"text":"I'm encouraged by that. At least it makes me feel like,"},{"time":910000,"text":"to some extent, it is becoming self-evident."},{"time":913000,"text":"That we need an alternative to the automobile,"},{"time":915000,"text":"at least for those 50-mile trips and more,"},{"time":917000,"text":"so that the highways become usable in today's world."},{"time":920000,"text":"Thank you."}]}]}